<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jordana Brewster enjoyed another intimate date with her new beau Mason Morfit on Saturday.</p>

<p>Looking elegant in a mid-length black dress the 40-year-old actress held hands with the ValueAct Capital CEO and gazed at him in the middle of a busy restaurant in Santa Monica.</p>

<p>The couple then strolled down the street together enjoying the beach town ambiance.</p>

<p>Look of love: Jordana Brewster and new man Mason Morfit gazed at each other in the middle of a busy restaurant in Santa Monica on Saturday </p>

<p>Jordana - who is in the process of divorcing her husband Andrew Form - looked effortlessly gorgeous with her long brunette locks loose around her shoulders. </p>

<p>She wore some black sandals and a yellow gingham face mask for a pop of color. </p>

<p>Jordana's romance with Mason went public in mid-July just weeks after she filed for divorce from film producer Andrew after 13 years of marriage.</p>

<p>Jordana and her ex share two sons, a seven-year-old named Julian and a four-year-old named Rowan.</p>

<p>They became an item through her 2006 film The Texas Chainsaw Massacre: The Beginning, on which Andrew was a producer.</p>

<p>Date night: The couple then strolled down the street together enjoying the beach town ambiance</p>

<p>Hollywood beauty: The 40-year-old actress looked effortlessly good in a mid-length black dress and some elegant heels</p>

<p>'We started dating in secret - you know, hanging out in my trailer - because it would have been unprofessional otherwise,' she spilled to InStyle later.</p>

<p>He proposed on the one-year anniversary of their relationship and presented her with a 3.2 carat diamond engagement ring.</p>

<p>Six months after he popped the question the couple married on the Caribbean island Nevis, according to People magazine.</p>

<p>After their split a People source said: 'They have the utmost respect for each other. They remain committed to lovingly co-parent their two children as a team.'</p>

<p>Ex factor: Jordana's romance with Mason went public in mid-July just weeks after she filed for divorce from film producer Andrew Form (pictured here in June 2019) after 13 years of marriage</p>
